Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:35.61,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,If you have it in you, head down the road of trials.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:45.45,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,And show them what men can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:49.91,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,Burn bright like a true champion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.16,0:00:54.00,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,until the Star of the Giants is in your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:56.88,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,Go all out until you sweat blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:00:58.84,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,Don't wipe away your tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.09,0:01:03.68,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,Go, go, Hyuuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:07.51,OP/ED,,0,0,0,,Head to your future!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:28.57,Sign,,0,0,0,,[Episode 3]\N[Showdown With Sadaharu Oh]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's #4 in overall performance batter for you. {nc what's soujitsuko}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.12,0:01:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, when Oh-sama hits the ball, \Nit flies away like a ping pong ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand why you brought me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That there is Sadaharu Oh, \Nthe Hero of Koshien.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.89,0:01:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And the man who will soon rise \Nto the position of a shining star.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's do I care for "stars"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, are you really trying that hard \Nto attach me to baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-san, just because we share the same roots,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having to suffer \Nthrough the ordeals of baseball too. {ive completely forgotten what's happened in previous episodes tbh}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanagata!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good job and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask for a favor? Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But we came here first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I said get lost, so get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you guys getting carried away a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny you ask that! Takes some nerve \Nto be picking holes in Black Shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, let's do it! Are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You came later so piss off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shithead, you're messing with {\i1}us{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshi, don't look down on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-san, please keep going \Nand show me more of your batting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:02:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting. You wanna do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H003500&}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I rushed out into the field \Nand forgot to remove the cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh! The cast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But look, Oh-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What will we do \Nif someone gets hurt in a petty fight? {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not a petty fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the one most important fight in baseball, \Nfor the right to use the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You chill down too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"You chill down too," just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, we're leaving. {}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back and fight, you coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Hoshi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you wanna join our team \Nand beat that coward Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're trying to fight us, \Nyou don't have the nerve to take Oh on, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hanagata-san, \Ncan we really let him go like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. That guy is certainly \Non a collision course with Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! What's the point of this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, what's the matter, Hyuuma? \NDid something happen? Tell me what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Akiko, I can't take it anymore! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep torturing myself with baseball,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For dad's sake, \NI even agreed to wear this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I'm at my limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fed up with all baseball players!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They call him a star, but he's just a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:04:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wants to make a name for himself! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyuuma, what happened there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in telling you anyhow.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I swear - even without becoming that kind of star,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do what it takes to make you happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll tell father you want to quit.{no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Now that's a rare sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweets in our ran-down shack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad quit drinking, remember? \NSo he can now buy those.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, try some.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll probably pass.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't eat the sweets dad bought with money he used to spend on drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyuuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Akiko, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyuuma! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad quit drinking for me. \NSo I can't let dad down either.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyuuma, wanna go train again? {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyuuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do better! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not there yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You should take off the cast \Nand wipe yourself normally. {}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But... there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's asleep already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Akiko, don't do what you weren't asked to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But he should be allowed to remove it \Nat least when going to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Akiko, you stay out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Father... That's going too...{}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're cruel. So cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If mother was still alive, \Nshe'd definitely object it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Akiko, it's alright. \NI can't afford slacking off.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyuuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, goodnight now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you! I hate you, father! \NYou're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother. What did you ever find \Nin a man like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In this baseball demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lock it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lock it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Akiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:08:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You wench!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Akiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you didn't have any reason to hit her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, it's time for the morning pitching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, father! Please let Hyuuma \Nhave a break just today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can put up with you mistreating me, \Nbut when you also do that to Akiko, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Opposing me out of the sibling's solidarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Akiko is already having to put up \Nwith a lot of things ever since mom died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard enough for her as it is, \Nwith your drinking and baseball obsession! {nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut it, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyuuma, enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you should allow \Nyour children more freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already fed up with baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You imbeciles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're helping yourself to sake \Nwhenever something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But what should we do?!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You sassy bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not my child if you hate baseball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave and never come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?{}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyuuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when you're not addicted to drinking, \Nyou're addicted to baseball!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna see my dad like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyuuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him!{} My only friends are sake and baseball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know exactly how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me in that funny voice!{nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not touching baseball ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. However, our baseball is a means of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:10:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it's the means of waging war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of pulling the would-be stars \Ndown from their stardom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. We, the Black Shadows, \Nwill challenge Oh's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,With you as our champion.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshi-kun, with my help, your disgust for that coward Oh will hit him with full force!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Sadaharu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, you following me, a high school student \Neverywhere is troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please ease it off a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Oh-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,after you graduate next year, \Nsurely, you'll turn pro, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're enrolling in a college?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Which team will you join? {}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be Giants. {no clue what's first word}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's admirable! Giants, after all? {nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, answer me!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me first!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Hoshi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it feel nice \Nto shine as a hero of Koshien yourself? {}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Even though he's such a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! So why don't we beat him \Nright in front of the reporters?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're a fan of Giants, Oh-kun?{}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're joining Giants. Is that certain?{}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course it'll be Giants!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad said that the Giants \Nare a constellation shining in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But dad himself \Nfell from that constellation once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So the next player to climb \Nto that glorious constellation is Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How about that? \NDo you want to confront Oh, Hoshi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather together that frustration \Nyou've accumulated up to now {}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and unleash it all at once at Oh!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do that, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to set me after him so much? {to instigate; to incite; to spur on; to set (e.g. a dog after someone)​}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm being a delinquent, \NI would never be a helpless delinquent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be a delinquent who's strong in everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, we need to defeat \NOh's team spectacularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And let them report it to the whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, please give me a break! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, we're starting!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we're all ready!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but you're not having it your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-san, it was us who came first this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But you guys have just arrived, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Those bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Sunday the most important day \Nto control the field on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But how about this, Oh-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If we hold a match between our two teams, \Nboth could use it at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-san, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you guys are okay with it, \NI don't mind either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, it's settled! We'll decide \Nwho bats first with rock-paper-scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take the field first! {taking the field first; batting second​}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:13:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Hoshi-kun, pitch for us, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds exciting! \NAlright! I'll be an umpire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hoshi! Give them hell! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Crap, I'm still wearing the cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really don't wanna take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that by taking it off, \NI'll sever myself completely from dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll pitch it with the cast on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Play ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,2-0!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike! Batter out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, it was kinda impossible \Nto catch the timing.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk. That loose ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you'll hit it! We know you will! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-san, punish their insolence!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe in you, Oh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That pitcher is not throwing \Nany ordinary balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if he was deliberately driving slowly \Na sports car that can go all 300km/h.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How unusual...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met a pitcher like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, \Nit's not some ordinary slow ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:16:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When it actually reaches the batter's box, \Nit gets even more eerie and powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,2-0!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, hey! The Hero or Koshien!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-san, don't let us down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hit it!{nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If a pitcher throws as hard as he can, \Nbut can only achieve this much speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,he's not supposed to have \Nso much precise control over it.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Timeout.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Timeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Why isn't Oh hitting?{}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of the prodigy Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He could see that it's no mere slow ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But could it really be \Nbecause of that weird cast?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even in my wildest dreams I'd be throwing fastballs even at one tenth of Hoshi's speed.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's flying over there! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we've seen it! \NYou hit a home run for us!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager, it's much different \Nfrom what you told us!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't Hoshi take off that cast?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot. He's not the kind of guy \Nwho'd take it off even if you force him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good enough as it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going exactly according to my plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just confined in the cast that only lets me \Nthrow at one tenth of my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, how did that bastard \Npull off that enormous home run? {}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Umpire! We're changing the pitcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshi for Toyama. {I know for certain it's not what he says but ive no clue what this toeba}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say? Changing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be alright, let me pitch more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can suppress every other batter \Nwith my control alone!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disappoint, \Nbut that's not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't afford being smashed \Nby another huge home run like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...{}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Suit yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You call yourself a man after that? \NWell, if you wanna flee, go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Flee? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just the type I thought him to be.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Play ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-san, smash them again!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Timeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:18:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Timeout!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done. You pitched four good balls \Nand now we have bases loaded. {base on balls; walk; pass​}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Pitcher change!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right fielder​ Hoshi will pitch once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hoshi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not feeling confident enough \Nagainst Oh even with bases loaded?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, I wanna compete with my true strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as I hate baseball, I hate \Nbeing made fun of and losing even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Play!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm not letting you hit \Na home run like the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you my true fastball!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta stop them! \NAt least the one on the third base... {not a single word tbh}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an unbelievable blazing fastball...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand is still a little numb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.13,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Saburo?{} \NWe have a pitcher and we have a catcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Third base is in the catcher's responsibility! {again no clue what's santei, this word was also in the cursed line at 20:17; imma assume nobody fucking knows the rules of baseball}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How gutless are you \Nto be afraid to pick up the ball?!{g; nc whats haba}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, that was scary.\NHis ball is that incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We've no need for wimps like you. \NGet lost! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You don't get it, Hanagata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I'm covering my eyes with my mitt is because I can't stand seeing anyone's poor play. {very unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this hack blabbering about?!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna do it? \NI'm 100 times better at fighting than at baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting. It'll be useful for me as a newbie delinquent to look at how senpai does that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Delinquent?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Umpire, if we let this delinquent team \Ncontinue playing the match,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-san's good name would end up smeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please interrupt the match at once. I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You started a brawl in the middle \Nof a sacred match!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I score you with forfeiting the match!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Seriously?{}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-san, let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys. Although it ended in this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,this was a very eventful \Nand moving day for me.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean me?{}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're smiling sincerely, \Nbut you aren't supposed to! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As a hero of Koshien, you couldn't respond to my ball with anything better than a bunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:22:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're pulling out, \NI want you say it clearly: "I lost!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even the renowned \Nheavy hitter from high school
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,can just quietly sneak back home \Nafter failing to hit my ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Oh-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshi-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's just my imagination,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but didn't you gain your baseball skills \Njust training with your coach and no one else?{hope he means this}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So what, even if I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.78,0:22:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, he is probably \Nan excellent coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.28,0:22:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But baseball is a team sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If, without understanding that truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,as a pitcher, you'd try to win \Nwith nothing but the strength of your ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.50,0:22:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,engulfed in that confidence, \Nyou'll forget to prepare for defense.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.68,0:22:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you hit a bunt? \NA commendable observation.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was still cheap!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.60,0:22:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why didn't you just swing at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could determine your line of pitching during the first two throws, I might've done that.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.18,0:22:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if I'd have let that real pitch of yours go by, the catcher would've been in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.37,0:22:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I opted out for a bunt, \Nrather than a riskier swing.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.19,0:23:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you just did it on the spur or the moment, \Nconcerned about the opponent catcher's safety?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.82,0:23:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I meant to say either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's meet again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.26,0:23:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost thoroughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.18,0:23:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I threw the ball \Nwith all my strength at our catcher,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.68,0:23:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd been protected \Nby Oh from the opposing team.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I never took the catcher's safety in consideration. {no clue waht's jijitsu}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.79,0:23:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm defeated... Completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Baseball is a severe sport!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But also a wonderful one!
